      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a great new home. It has been super reliable for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It's been well-loved and well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that drives like a dream, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
